## ğŸ¯ Type Generation

Types are automatically generated from your Go structs:

```go
// internal/types/user.go
type User struct {
    ID    int    `json:"id"`
    Name  string `json:"name"`
    Email string `json:"email"`
}
```

Generates TypeScript:

```typescript
// frontend/src/types/generated.d.ts
export interface User {
  id: number
  name: string
  email: string
}
```

And API client:

```typescript
